<h2>
    Introduction to Trout Fishing in Southern Oregon
</h2>
<p>
    Southern Oregon is a haven for anglers who appreciate stunning landscapes, clean mountain waters, and a chance to reel in beautiful trout. <strong>Medford</strong> serves as a perfect basecamp to access world-class trout fisheries—from remote alpine lakes to accessible city streams.
</p>
<h3>
    Why Medford is Perfect for Trout Anglers
</h3>
<p>
    Medford’s proximity to a diverse range of fisheries means you can go from urban ponds to alpine lakes in under an hour. Whether you're a fly-fishing purist or a weekend warrior with a spinning rod, there's water nearby that matches your style.
</p>
<h3>
