</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Rainbow Trout</strong>: Commonly stocked and widely distributed
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Cutthroat Trout</strong>: Native to Oregon, found in clear, cold streams
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Brown Trout</strong>: More elusive, found in deeper or slower-moving water
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Brook Trout</strong>: Found in higher-elevation lakes and small creeks
    </li>
</ul>
